name: Cosmic Conquest of the Yellow Toad

metadata.name: Cosmic Conquest of the Yellow Toad #1/6
metadata.description:
As a street artist from the UK, I'm excited to present "Cosmic Conquest of the Yellow Toad," a captivating digital artwork created using a mix of Photoshop and AI assistance from midjourney. Introducing  my artwork created for the love of "$turbo." Limited to only six editions, this high-resolution NFT features a stunning yellow toad painting framed within a digital display. I'm grateful for the support of my friends and supporters, and I hope you enjoy this unique piece.

Join me on this artistic journey as I explore the convergence of traditional and digital art. With "Cosmic Conquest of the Yellow Toad," I offer a rare and exclusive NFT experience. Embrace the wonder and inspiration of this limited edition artwork, and become a part of my artistic evolution. Thank you for your ongoing support, and I hope this piece leaves a lasting impression on you.
